  "body": "### Proposed Change\r\n\r\nA concern people have had about auto merging draft EIPs without editor review (#5641) was that they might be low quality, and might reflect poorly on EIPs as a whole. Therefore, to enable this change to happen, I propose this be added as a tiled background image on all Draft EIPs:\r\n\r\n![draftv2.png](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45835846/217897048-a7b7800d-0744-4a97-8a4f-91ce8fda179a.png)\r\n",
